  "texts": [
    "The data from 2020 onwards contains multiple times more content from other periodicals besides Delfi (see S1 File for detailed distribution of Ekspress data).We chose sentence as the unit of analysis, instead of e.g.",
    "paragraph or article, for three reasons.",
    "The length of articles varies greatly, as does the length of a paragraph across articles, and some articles lack paragraph splits.",
    "Secondly, longer text sequences may include multiple stances, which may confuse both human annotators and machine classifiers.",
    "Thirdly, the computational model, BERT, has an optimal input length limit below the length of many longer paragraphs."
  ],
